&lt;p&gt;A24 is seeking a strategic, results-driven manager to lead the LA Creative Marketing team&#39;s paid media creative operations — spanning asset production, media strategy execution, and campaign analytics across theatrical releases. Ideal candidates will bring deep expertise in paid media ecosystems, from planning and placement to performance analysis, alongside a strong command of emerging ad tech, AI-driven tools, and data-informed decision-making. This role requires a confident leader who can independently drive campaigns from brief to delivery while shaping the broader paid media vision for the team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is based in Los Angeles.&lt;/p&gt;
