&lt;li&gt;Own the full paid media production lifecycle across all campaigns — from creative development through placement, delivery, and post-campaign learnings — spanning formats like display, high-impact takeovers, OOH, programmatic, social, and earned media&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring a strong creative vision and sharp sense of taste, setting the bar for what great work looks like across campaigns and raising the quality of every touchpoint&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conceive and execute first-to-market creative campaigns that tell bold stories, connect with audiences, and drive KPIs — bringing a sharp POV and clear creative direction to internal teams, agencies, and external partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft compelling creative briefs and presentations that inspire great work and drive alignment and buy-in across stakeholders at all levels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage freelancers, vendors, and agency partners end-to-end, with the operational rigor to keep simultaneous campaigns on time, on brand, and at a high creative bar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with media planning and buying teams to crack how creative can work harder across placement, platform, and audience — and translate campaign performance and media insights into sharper creative decisions on future work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply emerging tools and technologies to unlock new creative possibilities and drive smarter, faster, and more scalable campaign workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead cross-functional collaboration with media, post, international, and platform partners, navigating blockers and driving decisions that move campaigns forward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor junior team members and establish best practices for production, media operations, and data-informed creative work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
