&lt;p&gt;A24 is looking for a Coordinator to provide support to our global licensing team focused on providing television and film content to broadcast and platform partners around the world. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Responsibilities will include TV &amp;amp; Film sales market coordination, client servicing support, operations maintenance, schedule management, availability tracking and report production, and general departmental administrative tasks. This person is acutely detail-oriented, hungry to support a growing business, with a client-focused mindset.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Please note this role is based in NY and candidates must be able to work in-person from our NY office.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Initial Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
