&lt;p&gt;A24 is engaging an independent contractor to manage the merchandise production process for a popular adult animated television series. The contractor will apply their professional expertise and independent judgment to oversee product development, manufacturing, and logistics, operating autonomously to deliver results within agreed timelines. This is a part time 6-month engagement, with the possibility to extend as projects expand or continue.&lt;/p&gt;
