&lt;li&gt;Manage talent participation across all press activities including interviews, press days, premieres, film festivals, talk shows, and promotional tours, ensuring a seamless and well-supported experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a deep understanding of each talent&#39;s preferences, priorities, and working style to anticipate needs and navigate dynamics with care and professionalism&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Film Leads to prepare thorough briefing materials and talking points for talent ahead of media appearances&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support Senior Publicists and Film Leads in developing and executing strategic PR campaigns across A24&#39;s film slate, taking ownership of assigned titles from campaign launch through release&lt;/li&gt;
