&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain strong media relationships; proactively identify new press opportunities and craft pitches that drive coverage across titles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with International Publicity, Grassroots, and Events teams to align efforts on specialty and awards campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage key press materials – including one-pagers, key set images, and clips – in coordination with Publicity Coordinators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Staff publicity events, including press days, screenings, film festivals, and awards-related events; availability for after-hours and weekend coverage required&lt;/li&gt;
