&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary finance liaison to the TV Development, Production and Business Affairs teams across LA, New York, and the UK — attending greenlight meetings, participating in production planning sessions, and proactively flagging financial and operational risks.&lt;/li&gt;
