&lt;p&gt;A24 is seeking a TV Legal Delivery Associate, an exciting new role working closely with our Post &amp;amp; Legal teams. Reporting to the Legal Delivery Manager, this role will independently manage day-to-day legal delivery workflows for our original television slate, including scripted, unscripted, animation and UK-based projects, while escalating complex issues and supporting consistent delivery standards across A24’s Film and TV businesses. This role can be based in our New York or Los Angeles office.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
